metadata.description:
I was overwhelmed with support on my latest free drop 'promises', which landed on the trending page on Spinamp, and generated over 13 secondary sales. For a free drop I think that's incredible, so thank you to anyone who messaged me kind words or collected.

I'm on a roll right now with music, writing so many different genres and honestly some of the dopest art i've ever created.

This track (bubbles) being one of them. I grew up listening to trance and was one of the first genres that introduced me to dance music, so it only felt natural to draw from the genre with this one.

Enjoy! Thanks again for your support, it means the world and is pushing me to write more and more. <3
